   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Apollonous to Kolulis her brother, many greetings.  As soon as you receive the letter, go to the wheel and pull down the whole wall and move the machinery to the ... place.  As for the rest, take care to keep well. Ninth year of Tiberius [Claudius] Caesar Augustus Germanicus Imperator, Mecheir 17th, dies Augustus.</ab>
         </div>
